  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1244211/" class="title-link">其实了解过去不难</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1244211"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/hami8009/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1197566-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hami8009/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">哈米玻玻</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-11-21"
      class="main-meta">2007-11-21 12:47:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1244211_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  王立群也好,孟庆实\易中天也好,他们都在很大程度上将历史说得更平民化,很生动,很形象,让人能饶有兴致地看下去,听下去,历史能以这样的方式被更多的人所接受,关注,热爱,其实是一件不错的事.毕竟,以史为鉴可以知兴替.  这本书把史记中所牵到的汉武帝时期大部分历史人物都说到了,说...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1244211/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
